title: Trailer Alert: Baahubali 2 Is A Visual Treat
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 16 . 2017 
The much awaited trailer of Baahubali 2 is finally out and it will blow your mind with its spectacular visuals. If the trailer is anything to go by, this one is going to be bigger, better and a lot more intense than the first one. Weâ€™re not sure why this was released abruptly, but rumours suggest that Malayalam trailer got leaked, which is why the makers decided to put this out there asap. Check it out.
